HEADWORD: Mesolabe
<hw>Mes"o*labe</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>mesolabium</ets>, Gr. <?/; <grk>me`sos</grk> middle + <?/ to
take.]</ety> <def>An instrument of the ancients for finding two mean
